OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCoastal low
OL,6,Fcloud returns once more to affect most
OL,7,Fplaces overnight. Remaining dry with a
OL,8,Fgentle northeasterly breeze, wind
OL,9,Feasing and becoming light in places.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FA cloudy morning for many,
OL,12,Fthough becoming bright with some hazy
OL,13,Fsunshine by the afternoon as the low
OL,14,Fcloud retreats to the coast. The
OL,15,Fnortheasterly breeze persists
OL,16,Fthroughout the day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
