OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FLargely
OL,6,Fsettled with a mix of sunny spells and
OL,7,Fcloudy periods. Breezy along the
OL,8,Fcoast. A cooling trend by the weekend
OL,9,Fbut temperatures remain above average.
